{"tid":417980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新任中聯辦主任：港獨嚴重違法、絕不可能","createTime":"2017-09-29T07:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T05:09:12.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cd321267b2f0bfc1eead3c56317cc41a1e87ad","tid":417980,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170929/s00001/fccacbb499457e23ea1013dad544671f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170929%2Fs00001%2Ffccacbb499457e23ea1013dad544671f.jpg&h=ce0b86bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任王志民下午出席新聞界慶祝國慶酒會時表示，中央會貫徹落實一國兩制方針，指港獨「嚴重違法，絕不可能」。他又以廣東話祝賀港人國慶及中秋節愉快。<br />\n<br />\n王志民表示，他去年3月在北京工作時，已被傳媒問及港獨問題，他當時回答指港獨是「嚴重違法，絕不可能」。他進一步解釋：「《基本法》的第一條它（港獨）就違反了，《基本法》的9章160條，那就全部都違反了，這難道不是嚴重違法嗎？」他又說，中國960萬平方公里領土上，來自「全球全世界」、包括700多萬港人在內的「全體國人」，對港獨都是「零空間」、「零容忍」，故港獨是「絕不可能」。<br />\n<br />\n王指自香港回歸以來，中央「一直堅定不移貫徹一國兩制方針」，強調全面準確落實港人自港、高度自治，嚴格按照憲法和《基本法》辦事，不論是誰在香港中聯辦或不同港澳工作機構任職，都是「一個目標、一個方針」，按照國家主席習近平一直所強調，堅持一國兩制方針、確保一國兩制在香港實現「不變形、不走樣」，沿正確方向前進。<br />\n<br />\n對於與泛民主派的關係，王志民說廣泛聯繫社會各界人士是一直是中聯辦的重要職責之一，今後會繼續這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n王志民在發言前先以廣東話祝港人「國慶節、中秋節愉快」，最後亦分別以廣東話說「多謝大家」。"},{"pid":"1c315aec37af58eda7a29a77bb9f9ee528c116a3","tid":417980,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"咁捨得拉人未"},{"pid":"d23ccb32cbb97076014b779ebbbc16527eeea7ff","tid":417980,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:27:58.000Z","msg":"嚴重違法？ 咁刑罰係乜東東？"},{"pid":"16225a2a1b378792c1955cb9b8a8ddb8da4435ab","tid":417980,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"違反基本法罰d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec505c5dda398a33b7c6699731ff56b9d4733cf","tid":417980,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>違反基本法罰d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n至多咪罰唔比參選"},{"pid":"9e7d48875b3c620bd0f6294672e6c88a63cd1bc2","tid":417980,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"違左邊條法?"},{"pid":"9650587f89cd7506901945c47992a351f7aad3cc","tid":417980,"uid":46700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲人只會講你犯法去兇鳩你<br />\n但佢連到底犯咩法都講唔出口<br />\n<br />\n倒不如直接啲講唔聽大陸話就即時槍決啦"},{"pid":"410e20296ed21af4a38277a03096eca3120b97ed","tid":417980,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"點嚴重法?<br />\n咁咩係輕微違法?"},{"pid":"49a18cd25388f049397d5885bee1a5837cc3eca6","tid":417980,"uid":47359,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:33:50.000Z","msg":"合法就合法。違法就違法。咩叫嚴重違法?"},{"pid":"ad3943f9288ac92458a0f7cdcd67bcfc85620e43","tid":417980,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:34:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩訓醒 港獨份子拉左未"},{"pid":"6c6d90148ee2df7314c2f60e1400e0c95cdb72db","tid":417980,"uid":82929,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"美國獨立，英國都會話違法架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n法律為權貴服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n革命就係打破權貴管治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過歷史上革命都要流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下獨派有冇吉士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0194788582ade27efef891ef6a2a36dad6f0b90b","tid":417980,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:35:30.000Z","msg":"鼓吹殺人犯唔犯法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0696849874aac7556fa7af807b3b6ca6374699ea","tid":417980,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩訓醒 港獨份子拉左未</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf358c3931fb547074da79205621b9c6c00f6686","tid":417980,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"捉你入西九處決啦"},{"pid":"807384b6a617c6f922d307fe7f649a01d37bd11e","tid":417980,"uid":63782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"咁幾時拉鳩晒選管會班冚家剷？<br />\n基本法講明&ldquo;香港特別行政區永久性居民依法享有選舉權和被選舉權&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9315445440ec0f471fd1f263a3e47d259dea6abb","tid":417980,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"呢條友一日食幾多支煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd5e3c5c446328d92ed4fa741b4383f73597f33","tid":417980,"uid":21035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:40:34.000Z","msg":"咁仲唔拉哂佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0e4e60aff0d8e5ba2b5f8c7acc87239eca08f2","tid":417980,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>合法就合法。違法就違法。咩叫嚴重違法?</blockquote><br />\n依家係直接公開干預香港事務<br />\n以前都會帶吓頭盔"},{"pid":"d9509ab4eb8912ecd25d9ee3f9682d8e5143af7b","tid":417980,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"條友一定又係江派"},{"pid":"878538a7b00c44c688d297e0dc210c92de9225fa","tid":417980,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"708723f1fcd71924d98cd9731bf5411b1293f087","tid":417980,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢條友一日食幾多支煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食到D焦油搞到佢棚牙爛晒咁<br />\n<br />\n行埋去2米內都應該比陣支那劣煙味攻死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b982914fec346087200b3ed64cd90b827a636afd","tid":417980,"uid":2404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"新主任好野，毛主席都敢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e698c3b0220aabd11911d189dbddc299685600","tid":417980,"uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"我平日都可以算係嚴重守法"},{"pid":"59f00d8ae2df61906d587aab4dae483012e1adda","tid":417980,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>合法就合法。違法就違法。咩叫嚴重違法?</blockquote><br />\n依家係直接公開干預香港事務<br />\n以前都會帶吓頭盔</blockquote><br />\n垃圾行政長官唔敢嘈"},{"pid":"aaf5c819ac53761344afd8ff32e0b0bf1924ecdb","tid":417980,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c2e5ca4cc52bc31067a27afc8b3881b57f35771","tid":417980,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"咁拉人啦，唔好講廢話"},{"pid":"a2b931af389253627809f3cf540500ca9068a9e8","tid":417980,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:46:49.000Z","msg":"中聯辦主任王志民出席《蘋果》不獲邀的新聞界國慶酒會前，先透過傳媒祝市民中秋節、國慶快樂。<br />\n<br />\n他回應港獨問題時重申，去年3月他回應同一問題的說法：「嚴重違法，絕不可行」，他解釋港獨主張就違反了《基本法》第一條，故9章160條的基本法全都違法，並反問「不是嚴重違法嗎？」，並稱港獨在中國960萬平方公里土地上、全球全世界都零空間。<br />\n<br />\n他亦提到，回歸以來中央都強調全面準確落實港人治港，高度自治，嚴格按憲法和《基本法》辦事，無論誰人在中聯辦，還是不同的港澳機構都是同一目標、同一方針，即是按國家主席習近平強調的，堅持一國兩制方針不動搖不變形、確保香港一國兩制實行不走樣不變形。<br />\n<br />\n最後王志民表示，廣泛連繫各界是中聯辦的主要職責，一直都是這麼做，亦會繼續這樣做，稱會接觸包括泛民的社會各界人士。"},{"pid":"1c56f8360af334789ba3bd784ec30f0b56a20656","tid":417980,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://stati